09/03/2011
BELGRADE, Serbia -- Police in Novi Sad searched the home of war crimes fugitive Goran Hadzic's former driver on Tuesday (March 8th), looking for evidence that could lead to determining Hadzic's whereabouts. He and Ratko Mladic are the two last remaining war crimes indictees sought by The Hague tribunal. (RTS, Beta, B92 - 08/03/11)
